# ========== CONFIGURATION & SECRETS ==========
## Local / environment-specific configuration (should not be committed)
application-*.yml
application-*.yaml
application-*.properties
.env
*.env
secrets/
*.p12
*.jks
*.key

## But keep the main application.yml (if exists) – uncomment if needed
!application.yml
!application.yaml
!application.properties

